#: ../source/docs/development-environment/BT/pb.rst:71
#: 4dcead884e214641b1aca7c019692929
msgid ""
"在 C/C++标签页的 Preprocessor SymbolsDefine 里面，开发者可以改变对应的预编译"
"宏："
msgstr ""
"In the C/C++ tab, under \"Preprocessor Symbols -> Define\", developers can "
"change the corresponding precompiled macros:"

#: ../source/docs/development-environment/BT/pb.rst:73
#: 26c3523849d540548e847b29cabb3639
msgid ""
"CFG_SLEEP_MODE=PWR_MODE_SLEEP ：使能低功耗模式，固件程序执行过程中， 会在空闲"
"过程进入睡眠，睡眠之后调试器无法进行调试跟踪，断点也失效。"
msgstr ""
"CFG_SLEEP_MODE=PWR_MODE_SLEEP: Enables low-power mode. During firmware "
"execution, the device enters sleep mode when idle. After entering sleep "
"mode, the debugger cannot perform debugging or tracing, and breakpoints "
"become invalid."

#: ../source/docs/development-environment/BT/pb.rst:74
#: e41f615b05584cf6a6751fb3f93d9bc5
msgid ""
"CFG_SLEEP_MODE=PWR_MOD_ENO_SLEEP ：关闭低功耗模式，固件程序执行过 程中，处理"
"器一直处于唤醒状态。"
msgstr ""
"CFG_SLEEP_MODE=PWR_MOD_ENO_SLEEP: Disables low-power mode. During firmware "
"execution, the processor remains awake."

#: ../source/docs/development-environment/BT/pb.rst:75
#: 3fdfd3e25e8740bebab94500608bb728
msgid "DEBUG_INFO=1：使能调试信息，默认通过串口输出：P9(Tx),P10(Rx)"
msgstr ""
"DEBUG_INFO=1: Enables debug information output. By default, debug "
"information is output through the serial port: P9 (Tx), P10 (Rx)."

#: ../source/docs/development-environment/BT/pb.rst:76
#: 74771c6403d14a9fb5840292df310581
msgid "DEBUG_INFO=0：关闭调试信息"
msgstr "DEBUG_INFO=0: Disables debug information output."

